'''Cricket Board of Maldives''' is the official [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of the sport of [[cricket]] in [[Maldives]]. Its current headquarters is in [[Male]], [[Maldives]]. Cricket Board of Maldives is the Maldives representative at the [[International Cricket Council]] and is an affiliate member and has been a member of that body since 2001. It is also a member of the [[Asian Cricket Council]]. 

