{{infobox country at games | NPC = KUW | NPCname = Kuwait Paralympic Committee | games = Paralympics | year = | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = | location = | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 12 | silver = 17 | bronze = 21 | officials = | appearances = | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Kuwait|competition=Summer Paralympics|begin_year=1980|end_year= }} | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Kuwait]]''' made its '''[[Paralympic Games]]''' début at the [[1980 Summer Paralympics]] in [[Arnhem]], with a delegation in [[track and field]]. The country has participated in every subsequent edition of the [[Summer Paralympics]], but has never taken part in the [[Winter Paralympics]].<ref>[http://www.paralympic.org/Sport/Results/search.html?npc=KUW&gender=all&medal=all&sport=all&games=all Kuwait at the Paralympics], [[International Paralympic Committee]]</ref>
Kuwaiti competitors have won a total of 49 Paralympic medals, of which 12 gold, 17 silver and 21 bronze..<ref>[http://www.paralympic.org/Sport/Results/search.html?npc=KUW&gender=all&medal=all&sport=all&games=all Kuwait at the Paralympics], International Paralympic Committee</ref>
