'''FC Nasaf-2 Qarshi''' ({{lang-uz|Насаф-2 Карши}}) is a [[Uzbekistan]]n [[association football]] club based in [[Qarshi]]. Nasaf-2 is the farm club of [[Nasaf Qarshi]]. Currently it plays in [[Uzbekistan First League|First League]].

==History==
Nasaf-2 was formed with intention to feed and provide [[Nasaf Qarshi]] with young successful players. Club plays in [[Uzbekistan First League|First League]], conference ''West'' and participate in [[Uzbek Cup]].

On 20 July 2012, the current head coach of Nasaf-2, Shuhrat Toshpulatov was appointed as assistant coach of Nasaf Youth team and resigned his position at Nasaf-2. Club had appointed Rakhmatulla Muhammedrakhimov as new head coach.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fcnasaf.uz/view/823/|title=Замена тренера у “Насаф-2”|publisher=fcnasaf.uz|accessdate=|date=2012-07-20}}{{dead link|date=February 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

